

C) Lower & Upper
================


— Currently the Database which we are using is Case Insensitive but Some of the Databases are Case Sensitive so in that case Lower and Upper is Used




— Lower Example

SELECT LOWER('SQL Champion Program');

Output —


+-------------------------------+
| LOWER('SQL Champion Program') |
+-------------------------------+
| sql champion program          |
+-------------------------------+






— Upper Example 

SELECT UPPER('SQL Champion Program');

Output —


+-------------------------------+
| UPPER('SQL Champion Program') |
+-------------------------------+
| SQL CHAMPION PROGRAM          |
+-------------------------------+












